{"title":"北京的夜","authors":["阿列克斯·恰奇"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":10,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔阿尔巴尼亚〕阿列克斯·恰奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从没有见过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的夜晚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这不是夜晚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风暴雨般地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把他们不需要的东西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连根拔起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把他们需要的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设起来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么今天的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里星光灿烂？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个中国人的心里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有一颗星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不尽的星光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了这里的黑夜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天的北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它到那里去了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一切都永久成为过去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的宫殿一座座地平地升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦染红了人们的面颊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个中国都在前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能阻挡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这波涛万里的威力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进呀！永远前进呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的兄弟们……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们紧紧地拉着手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们紧紧地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉着朋友们的手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧世界就这样被消灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世界就这样被建起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心在对我说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世界永远属于我们！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们才向月宫派遣了使者；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就要飞向月宫报喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要把生命带到那里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为生命将会战胜一切。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这个城市里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远没有黑夜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔李宁来译　戈宝权校〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}